{
  "chapter": 15,
  "chapter_summary": "傅红雪从樵夫郑进口中得知燕南飞被杀的经过：一个天神般的巨人（苗天王）和公孙屠等人杀害了燕南飞，尸体被送往天龙古刹。傅红雪前去寻找，发现郑进和小桃子已被人灭口。在窄巷中，萧四无出现并救了傅红雪，两人讨论飞刀与正义之心的差别。傅红雪来到天龙古刹，遇到疯和尚，疯和尚以禅语暗示古刹即将倒塌、丧钟将响。傅红雪不顾危险，毅然前往。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zheng_jin",
      "text": "说下去。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_jin",
      "speaker_name": "郑进",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "说……说什么？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zheng_jin",
      "text": "那天我走了之后，你又看见了什么事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_jin",
      "speaker_name": "郑进",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我看见了很多事，可是我全都没有看清楚。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zheng_jin",
      "text": "那个用红剑的人后来怎么样了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_jin",
      "speaker_name": "郑进",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "他死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zheng_jin",
      "text": "他怎么会死的？是谁杀了他？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_jin",
      "speaker_name": "郑进",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "他本来不会死的。你赶着车走了之后，他替你挡住了那三个人。别人好像都不敢去碰他的剑，所以他也找个机会走了，走得可真快，简直就像一阵风一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_jin",
      "speaker_name": "郑进",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "只可惜他刚窜人道旁的树林，那道斩马的刀光，又忽然飞了出来。他虽然避开了第一刀，但是那个人第二刀又砍了下来，而且一刀比一刀快。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_jin",
      "speaker_name": "郑进",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "他看来简直就像是天神，就像是魔王一样，站在那里至少比任何人都高出一个头，耳朵上戴着金环，穿着身用兽皮做的衣服，手上提的那把刀，最少也有七八尺长。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zheng_jin",
      "text": "后来呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_jin",
      "speaker_name": "郑进",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "那个外号叫厨子的人，本来想把你那朋友斩碎了放在锅里煮的，可是本来在下棋的一个人却坚决反对，后来他们就将你那朋友的尸体，交给了天龙古刹的和尚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zheng_jin",
      "text": "天龙古刹在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_jin",
      "speaker_name": "郑进",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "听说就在北门，可是我没有去过，很少人到那里去过！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zheng_jin",
      "text": "他们交给了那个和尚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_jin",
      "speaker_name": "郑进",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "天龙古刹里好像只有一个和尚，是个疯和尚，听说他……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_zheng_jin",
      "text": "他怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_jin",
      "speaker_name": "郑进",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "听说他不但疯，而且还喜欢吃肉，人肉。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cha_guan_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "茶馆掌柜",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "他刚走了。这两天他总算是在这里说那故事，总要坐到天黑以后才走，可是今天走得特别早。而且他走得很匆忙，好像有什么急事要去做。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cha_guan_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "茶馆掌柜",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "那条巷子里有个他的老相好，好像叫小桃子，他一定是找她去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_li_hua_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "戴茉莉花的女人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "里面有张床，又软又舒服，再加上我和一盆热水，只要两钱银子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_li_hua_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "戴茉莉花的女人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我只有十七岁，可是我的功夫好，比小桃子还好。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_mo_li_hua_nv_ren",
      "text": "告诉我，小桃子在哪里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_li_hua_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "戴茉莉花的女人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "就在最后面靠右首的那一家。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_xiao_si_wu",
      "text": "一刀两命，好刀！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_si_wu",
      "speaker_name": "萧四无",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "真的好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_xiao_si_wu",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_si_wu",
      "speaker_name": "萧四无",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你当然看得出我并不是要杀你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_xiao_si_wu",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_si_wu",
      "speaker_name": "萧四无",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我只不过想要你再看看我的刀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_xiao_si_wu",
      "text": "现在我已看过！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_si_wu",
      "speaker_name": "萧四无",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你已看过我三次出手，还有两次是对你而发的。对于我的出手，世上已没有别人能比你更清楚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_xiao_si_wu",
      "text": "很可能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_si_wu",
      "speaker_name": "萧四无",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "叶开是你的朋友，你当然也看过他出手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_si_wu",
      "speaker_name": "萧四无",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "现在我只想问你一件事，你若不愿告诉我，我也不怪你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_xiao_si_wu",
      "text": "你问。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_si_wu",
      "speaker_name": "萧四无",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我的飞刀究竟有哪一点比不上叶开？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_xiao_si_wu",
      "text": "你出手暗算我两次，第一次虽尽全力，却在出手前就已发声示警；第二次虽未出声，出手时却留了两分力。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_xiao_si_wu",
      "text": "这只是因为你自己心里也知道不该杀我的，你根本没有非杀我不可的理由，所以你出手时，就缺少了一种无坚不摧的正气。叶开要杀的，却都是非杀不可的人，所以他比你强！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_si_wu",
      "speaker_name": "萧四无",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "就只这一点？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_xiao_si_wu",
      "text": "这一点就已足够，你就已永远比不上他！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_si_wu",
      "speaker_name": "萧四无",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你等着，总有一天我会比他强的，等到那一天，我一定要杀了你。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_xiao_si_wu",
      "text": "我一定等着你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_li_hua_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "戴茉莉花的女人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你打我，就表示你喜欢我，我知道你以后一定还会来找我的。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_li_hua_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "戴茉莉花的女人",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我一定等着你。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_feng_he_shang",
      "text": "大师往何处去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "疯和尚",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "从来处来，当然是往去处去。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_feng_he_shang",
      "text": "大师可知道天龙古刹往哪里走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "疯和尚",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你跟我来。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_feng_he_shang",
      "text": "你真的是个疯和尚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "疯和尚",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "疯就是不疯，不疯就是疯。也许真正疯的不是我，是你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_feng_he_shang",
      "text": "是我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "疯和尚",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你若不疯，为什么要去送死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_feng_he_shang",
      "text": "你知道我是谁？知道我要到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "疯和尚",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "完了完了，千年的古刹就要倒塌，人海中到处血腥，你叫和尚到哪里去？",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "疯和尚",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你要去死，就赶快去吧！有时活着的确还没有死了的好。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "疯和尚",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "这是丧钟。丧钟一响，就一定有人要死的！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "疯和尚",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你若不死，别人就要死了，你为什么还不赶快去死？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_feng_he_shang",
      "text": "我去。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15
    }
  ],
